message: Open all groups containing a visited item

Update requirements

- vue-test-utils: use shallow instead of shallowMount
- vue-loader: add webpack plugin

Remove unit specs depending on whether router present or not

Some decisions inside components are based on router presence.
Unit specs of these components usually contained specs with
mock router since it was simple to test. Nevertheless, sometimes
happens that although unit specs are passing, there is a bug
related to mode without router. It would be way too much complicated
to prepare unit tests for both modes so I prepared e2e tests
which will be responsible for testing these parts.
